mg_roflcopter
Your roflcopter team versus the opposite one.
The terriost team's roflcopter is red and ofcause the counter terrorist's roflcopters are blue.

There is also a LOL plane, but there is only one and it is in the middle of the map!

To get the fail sign (as seen on one of the pics) you must find the secret button to get the deagle!

There is 32 spawn points.
